data.description: Looking for a property to put some love into and turn into an investment or your home with rental income? This multi unit home is being sold AS IS. Owners have started renovations, but projects need to be completed. Kitchen has new cabinets and double oven installed, plus additional cabinets in starage ready to be added.  Some new windows in the home. A couple of rooms have their original hardwood floors. House is currently functioning as a one family. Upstairs apartment can be a 1 bedroom or 2 bedroom depending how you separate the rooms.
